legs.end_address: Yeşilırmak, Gaziosmanpaşa Blv. No:70, Tokat Merkez/Tokat, Turkey
legs.start_address: Çelebiler, Hastane Cd. No:15, 32040 Isparta Merkez/Isparta, Turkey

steps.html_instructions: Head northeast on Hastane Cd. toward Adil Hüsrev Çk.
Hastane Cd. turns right and becomes Hasan Fehmi Cd.
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Atatürk Blv.
Keep right at the fork to continue toward Afyon Konya Yolu/D300
Keep left and merge onto Afyon Konya Yolu/D300

Turn left onto Eskişehir Konya Yolu/D675
Continue to follow D675
Take the ramp onto Afyon Ankara Yolu/D260/E96

Take the ramp on the left onto Ankara Eskişehir Yolu/D200/D260/E90
Continue to follow D200/E90

Merge onto Ankara Çevre Yolu/O-20/E90 via the ramp to Gölbaşı/Konya/Samsun
Continue to follow Ankara Çevre Yolu/O-20
Continue onto Ankara Çevre Yolu Samsun Yolu Bağlantısı

Keep right at the fork, follow signs for Kırıkkale/Kayseri/Samsun and merge onto 19 Mayıs Blv./D200/E88
Continue to follow D200/E88
Continue straight onto Kırıkkale Çorum Yozgat Yolu
Take the ramp to Kırıkkale Tokat Yolu/D190

Turn left to stay on Kırıkkale Tokat Yolu/D190
Continue to follow D190

Slight right onto Tokat Amasya Yolu/D180
Continue to follow D180

Turn right onto Çeçenistan Cd.
Go through 2 roundabouts
At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit and stay on Çeçenistan Cd.

Enter the roundabout
Destination will be on the left
